subject: Horse Racing
organizations: Woodward Stakes at Saratoga Race Course
lead_paragraph: Havre de Grace held off a late bid by Flat Out and defeated males in her first attempt, winning the $750,000 Woodward Stakes at Saratoga Race Course on Saturday.
